PendingStatusForm is a Form
    title is "TriggerRunStatus"
    Layout
        single column
            PendingStatusInfo.PendingStatus
            visible when (PendingStatusInfo.ExceptionClass entered)
                PendingStatusInfo.ExceptionClass
            visible when (PendingStatusInfo.ResultMessage entered)
                PendingStatusInfo.ResultMessage
            visible when (PendingStatusInfo.ResultStack entered)
                PendingStatusInfo.ResultStack
            PendingStatusInfo.JVMShutdown
            visible when (PendingStatusInfo.AsyncRetryInfo entered)
                PendingStatusInfo.AsyncRetryInfo
